  "instructions": [
    "Heat the shortening in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the beef to the pot and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the onion, carrot, and potato to the pot and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the beef broth, black pepper, salt, and paprika to the pot and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer the stew for 1 hour.",
    "Use a spoon to skim off any excess fat that rises to the surface of the stew.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with fresh parsley if desired."
